    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable daily driver that\u2019s ready for its next chapter! This car is in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear from its years of service, but it still has plenty of life left to give. It\u2019s a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for dependable transportation at a great value. With a little bit of care, this vehicle will continue to be a trusty companion on the road!",
