    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m selling my reliable daily driver, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained, so it's totally ready for its next owner to hop in and go! It drives smoothly and still looks great parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a solid, dependable ride that won't let you down, this is the one. Feel free to message me\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 33800.0,
