      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine with only the minor, expected signs of road use that come with a well-loved car. Inside, you\u2019ll find a meticulously cared-for cabin featuring supple seating and a dashboard that remains free of cracks or fading. Under the hood, the engine runs strong and quiet, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule that ensures a smooth, confident ride. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions exactly as intended. It is a dependable, attractive choice for anyone seeking a high-quality driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
